@mattl Startup idea.  

LifeStyleBatteries dot com

“Simply upload a photo of your battery usage, and our advanced AI technology will give you 8 top tips to enhance the world around you!  Be your very best self!  We delight internet celebrities, and thought leaders world wide.”

@libreoffice @cl3mcg This information should be immediately ammended. 

There's no a startup dialog to choose UI, rather it is triggered from a link in Tips of The Day dialog.

If user disable ToTD than the dialog is no where except in menubar or hamburger bar.

@NeoH0_452 One regret I have is not talking to founders before launching my startup here.

If someone asks me what's your n1 tip for would-be Tunisian founders, it would be go abroad and perhaps hire from Tunisia.

Staying and failing is a lose-lose for you and your country.

@_breeeeen_ you don’t get into a startup for the salary, it’s for the equity—certainly not for the work life balance. 

The best tip: make your skillset/stack invaluable so that companies are actively looking for your type of profile 

Then the ball is in your court. Research is key 🔑

@agazdecki But what if as a startup founder, you need a person who have different approach and have different experience in their own field which can help you to grow your startup. 
I'm really confused I should go for co founder or not, I'm little worried about my startup😬😬
Any tip ?

@tipsonNM 🔥 Don't Give Up!
What comes easy won't last long, and what lasts long won't come easy.

#Motivation #startup #hustle #tips #mlm

@RCYalamala @cesilvam Do entrepreneurs even heed recommendations or "tips"? 😅

Having worked with startup and entrepreneurs, I know how messy their schedule is and how no matter how much we try to sort it out, they'll always do what they think is best. For them, 

instinct &gt; planning

@CharlesCalzia My best tips for start up funding: 

Talk and connect with people who have raised funds for their start ups(what worked, their strategies, advice)

Bring on guests on your podcast(who can speak to why VC's fund startups, learn about the funding industry)
